text: Casablanca bombings may refer to: * Bombing of Casablanca (1907), a French naval bombardment that marked the beginning of the French conquest of Morocco * 2003 Casablanca bombings, a series of suicide bombings in Casablanca, Morocco * 2007 Casablanca bombings, a series of suicide bombings in Casablanca, Morocco
title: Casablanca bombings
